  "prompt": "Is there any Part time universities in Hamburg where we can pursue MS?",
  "response": "Yes, there are several universities and institutions in Hamburg, Germany, where you can pursue a Master of Science (MS) degree on a part-time basis. Here are some options:\n\n1. **University of Applied Sciences Europe (UE) Berlin, Hamburg Campus**: Offers a range of programs, including some master\u2019s degrees, with flexible study options, including part-time.\n\n2. **University of Hamburg**: Offers a variety of master\u2019s programs, some of which can be pursued part-time. Check the specific program details for part-time availability.\n\n3. **Hamburg University of Technology (TUHH)**: Offers flexible study options for some of its master\u2019s programs, including part-time study possibilities.\n\n4. **HafenCity University Hamburg (HCU)**: Provides flexible study arrangements for some of its master\u2019s programs.\n\nAdditionally, if you are open to online or blended learning formats, several German universities offer part-time and flexible study options, including some in Hamburg. Always verify details with the university or program coordinator to ensure your specific needs can be accommodated.",
